8
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:53,210
You call that shooting?

9
00:00:53,210 --> 00:00:55,840
You see, a gun works like this.

10
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:58,260
Ah, I was in over my head!

11
00:00:58,260 --> 00:01:00,970
As long as ya get it now, sweetie.

12
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:02,810
Who the hell are you?

13
00:01:04,020 --> 00:01:05,310
Stop it.

14
00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:07,060
So you wanna get shot in the head too?

15
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:09,770
All I'm doing is telling you to stop it.

16
00:01:09,770 --> 00:01:10,940
What?

17
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:35,920
BEYOND - Episode 2
The legend of Satan the Devil.

18
00:01:46,850 --> 00:01:49,440
May I ask you a question?

19
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,440
Yeah.

20
00:01:50,730 --> 00:01:53,110
Master, you said you had to rescue this girl,

21
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:54,980
and that's why you smashed that guy to pieces.

22
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,530
"Rescue"?

23
00:01:57,030 --> 00:02:01,740
Does that perhaps fall under the concept
of "empathy" you spoke of the other day?

24
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:05,540
Rescuing someone in distress...

25
00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:08,000
I felt it was the human thing to do.

26
00:02:08,290 --> 00:02:10,250
You're not human, though, Master.

27
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:12,380
Good point.

28
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:16,130
I smashed that guy to pieces without
applying much strength at all.

29
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:19,010
You smashed him to atoms.

30
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,760
This appears to be more difficult than I expected.

31
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,510
She seems to be regaining consciousness.

32
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,480
Are you okay?

33
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,620
Please let me call you "Teacher"!

34
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:47,450
"Teacher"?

35
00:02:47,450 --> 00:02:48,700
Yes!

36
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:50,120
That last attack move you did...

37
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,920
Please teach it to Faye-chan, sir!

38
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:55,540
Teach it to you, you say...

39
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:56,920
But why?

40
00:02:56,920 --> 00:03:01,430
Actually, you see, I'm descended from
a long line of bounty hunters,

41
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:03,890
that started with my great-great-great-grandfather.

42
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:08,100
I'm so awkward and clumsy however
that I can't do anything right.

43
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:10,680
I wanna become stronger!

44
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:13,150
I understand how you feel, but I'm not sure if...

45
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:15,690
I'll tolerate any kind of strict regimen!

46
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:19,440
So please, pass some of your
skills to cute little Faye-chan!

47
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,740
This is a problem.

48
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:23,700
It's a simple thing to do, Master.

49
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,360
What?

50
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,370
You simply need to share your powers with her.

51
00:03:26,830 --> 00:03:28,620
How do I do that?

52
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:29,620
Faye-san,

53
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:32,330
