73
00:05:45,090 --> 00:05:47,630
Aw, come on, Teacher!

74
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:54,140
You gave me so much power that I'm
in a really good mood right now!

75
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:59,140
Yes, but the relationship between a teacher
and student should be much stricter.

76
00:06:00,730 --> 00:06:03,110
I-I'm so sorry, Teacher!

77
00:06:03,650 --> 00:06:04,520
Listen to me!

78
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:08,070
If you think that's the only way to become
stronger, you're sadly mistaken.

79
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:09,280
Yes!

80
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:12,950
True power lies in hard work!

81
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:15,370
Follow alongside me hopping like a bunny!

82
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:16,240
Yes, Teacher!

83
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:21,290
From here on, I won't go easy on you.

84
00:06:21,290 --> 00:06:22,170
It's strict training!

85
00:06:22,170 --> 00:06:25,090
Yes! So this is strict training, I see.

86
00:06:25,090 --> 00:06:26,960
Faye-chan is doing her best!

87
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,760
I feel like a frog, however.

88
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,640
You are not a frog! You're a bunny!

89
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,590
Change at once!

90
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,390
Yes.

91
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,810
Not that kind of bunny, a rabbit!

92
00:06:36,810 --> 00:06:38,680
Yes!

93
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:43,020
Please train me harder and
harder and harder, Teacher!

94
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:45,730
What frightening spirit she has.

95
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:50,200
Teacher! Faye-chan will work hard!

96
