When I see Faye-san and Master together,
I feel a strange sensation.

98
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,460
Hey, hey! Can't you keep going!?

99
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,300
Yes!

100
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:13,010
Where is he!? That virginity thief!

101
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:33,110
Found him!

102
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,740
Take this, Devil!

103
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,590
Cute.

104
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,830
Jump higher!

105
00:08:04,330 --> 00:08:05,700
Yes, Teacher!

106
00:08:12,530 --> 00:08:13,740
Shit!

107
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:15,240
I'm not letting this get to me!

108
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,840
The legend of the Black Angel?

109
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:32,960
Yes. Listening to Ren-chan's story reminded me of it.

110
00:08:32,970 --> 00:08:35,720
It's a story from the Vineria Kingdom.

111
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:38,720
They have a legend about a black angel
who is very similar to you, Teacher.

112
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,100
Long ago,

113
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,640
when the kingdom was attacked by something evil,

114
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:45,190
a black angel came down to them from the sky.

115
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:49,310
The sight of the terrifying creature
deeply disturbed the citizens,

116
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:52,900
but then a beautiful girl dispelled
the peoples concerns.

117
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:57,450
After saving the people, the angel turned into
a beam of light and returned to the sky.

118
00:08:57,450 --> 00:08:58,490
The end.

119
00:09:07,170 --> 00:09:11,040
Faye-chan only knows about that much of the story.

120
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:14,130
Well if that angel really is me, that would be great.

121
00:09:14,130 --> 00:09:15,510
He sounds like a really nice guy!

122
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:19,050
Master?

123
00:09:19,050 --> 00:09:23,430
Teacher you saved Little Faye though,
so of course you're a good person.

124
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:31,230
Sorry for the wait, patron.

125
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:33,860
I wish to ask a question.

126
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:36,320
What's up with you? Your voice sounds strange.

127
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:40,490
Faye-chan and her friends wanna know more
about the legend of the Black Angel.

128
00:09:40,490 --> 00:09:42,160
Where might we go to find some answers?

129
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:44,290
Ah! So that's why he's dressed like that.

130
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:46,960
If you want to know more about the
Black Angel legend, then look!

131
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,790
Go to that shrine over there.

132
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:17,070
O mighty Angel, please save Vineria!

133
00:10:17,070 --> 00:10:19,950
Hey, young woman, why are you crying?

134
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,330
The Angel?

135
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,750
The Angel!

136
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:33,290
So you've returned to us at last!

137
00:10:33,290 --> 00:10:34,790
I never lost faith in you!

138
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,960
"Returned"?

139
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:39,760
I've believed in you since I was a little child.

140
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,890
I believed that the Black Angel really existed,

141
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:44,300
and that he would protect us from harm!

142
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:47,970
Right now, our civilization faces a horrible crisis,

143
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:50,190
and in response, you've come to our aid!

144
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,650
Come, follow me, Black Angel!

145
00:10:53,650 --> 00:10:56,400
Come with me to our palace!

146
00:10:56,400 --> 00:11:00,280
Wah! But he's Faye-chan's Teacher!

147
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:02,200
My Teacher!

148
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,660
Here.

149
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:07,870
Your acolytes are welcome to come along as well.

150
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,080
Acolytes?

151
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,540
Faye-chan is his woman!

152
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,510
So this is your king?

153
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:25,050
Nice to meet you.

154
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:29,520
Umm, I mean, I'm not here to harm you.

155
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,890
Why are you frightened, Father?

156
00:11:31,890 --> 00:11:34,850
This is the Black Angel of ancient legend!

157
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:39,070
He heard my prayer and answered
it with his holy return!

158
00:11:39,530 --> 00:11:40,780
I see!

159
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:43,570
If Chime says so, there must be no mistake!

160
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:50,750
So you think I really am the actual
Black Angel of legend?

161
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:53,710
With you back on our side, we
will certainly win the war!

162
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:54,870
The war?

163
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:57,710
Father! Can we have a banquet celebration tonight?

164
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:59,380
Splendid, splendid.

165
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:00,300
Listen, subjects!

166
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:02,470
A banquet tonight! A banquet!

167
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,680
Oh, Teacher, you're so amazing!

168
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:09,470
Faye-chan is proud to be the woman
of such an amazing man!

169
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:12,060
