170
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:24,240
Were conducting a sacred banquet
today in honor of the Angel!

171
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,860
You must return from where you came!

172
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:27,530
Gimme a frickin' break.

173
00:12:27,530 --> 00:12:29,330
Don't you have any idea who he really is?

174
00:12:29,330 --> 00:12:31,540
He's the Black Angel of the Vineria Kingdom.

175
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:33,120
"Black Angel", you say?

176
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:35,210
Snap out of your fairytale!

177
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:39,210
Just look at him! He's the Dark
Devil, who destroys everything!

178
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:41,000
How dare you speak such foolishness!

179
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:43,720
Princess Chime says so, and she's never wrong!

180
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:46,720
But you can be wrong for believing her!

181
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,140
What's your problem?

182
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:51,890
Speaking ill of the Black Angel is the same
as speaking ill of Princess Chime!

183
00:12:51,890 --> 00:12:54,850
Someone! Throw this intruder out of our kingdom!

184
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:14,500
Jeez!

185
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:16,960
Why are the people of this kingdom so clueless?

186
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:20,790
I guess my only choice is to strike
first before anyone's the wiser.

187
00:13:31,850 --> 00:13:33,220
What the hell is this?

188
00:13:33,220 --> 00:13:34,270
The sewer?

189
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:39,730
Dont give in, Eva!

190
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:44,440
Teacher, were in different rooms?

191
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:49,160
I've prepared a special room on
the third floor for the Angel.

192
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:51,490
His acolytes may stay in this room.

193
00:13:51,490 --> 00:13:53,370
Really? You're no fun.

194
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,990
Very well.

195
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,370
So, Master, good night.

196
00:13:57,620 --> 00:14:00,250
Ah, good night to you as well.

197
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:01,840
Angel, come this way.

198
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:08,420
I was hoping Teacher would make
love to me again tonight.

199
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:12,800
Faye-chan, how about I give you
a much nicer bed than that?

200
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:21,730
Aren't we there yet?

201
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:24,270
I don't want anyone to disturb us.

202
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,230
Disturb?

203
00:14:25,230 --> 00:14:27,070
I'll explain later.

204
00:14:35,540 --> 00:14:37,580
Where is he, where is he?

205
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:39,870
Looks like Princess Chime has made her decision.

206
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,750
Yeah.

207
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,170
This way, Angel.

208
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:51,680
The s-special room... Don't you
think its a little too far away.

209
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,140
Come, this way.

210
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:57,810
Princess Chime?

211
00:14:58,180 --> 00:15:01,600
I ordered everyone to stay away from this room.

212
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:02,940
Why?

213
00:15:03,690 --> 00:15:08,280
Angel, after you arrived here, I reached my decision.

214
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:09,820
Decision?

215
00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:10,990
What kind of decision?

216
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:15,450
I don't want my beloved Veneria
to get entangled in this matter.

217
00:15:15,830 --> 00:15:18,830
The fate of this kingdom is linked to my fate.

218
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:21,290
I still don't really get the situation here.

219
00:15:21,290 --> 00:15:23,580
For now, just for tonight

220
00:15:23,580 --> 00:15:25,540
please make love to me!

221
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:28,170
What did you just say?

222
00:15:28,170 --> 00:15:30,800
I know it's odd for a woman to ask you this...

223
00:15:32,890 --> 00:15:37,470
but for tonight please do my bidding
without asking any questions.

224
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:54,320
Angel... I've always wanted this to happen.

225
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:42,580
Come inside.

226
00:17:30,170 --> 00:17:31,380
Hey!

227
00:17:32,460 --> 00:17:33,210
Hey!

228
00:17:33,670 --> 00:17:34,510
Hey!

229
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:36,220
Hey!

230
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:43,720
Please wake me up more gently. Huh?

231
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,100
Ms. Policewoman?

232
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,850
Don't "Ms. Policewoman'' me!

233
00:17:46,850 --> 00:17:50,190
I'm sorry I left without thanking you properly.

234
00:17:50,190 --> 00:17:51,730
I don't care about that!

235
00:17:51,730 --> 00:17:53,780
I think I might know the answer but I'll ask anyway.

236
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:56,610
How do I go about killing you!?

237
00:18:00,780 --> 00:18:02,830
By the way, do you know where Chime is?

238
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:05,120
The princess who was here with me...

239
00:18:06,210 --> 00:18:08,870
That's what I want to talk to you about.

240
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:11,250
Clean out your ears and listen up.

241
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:11,710
Yes?

242
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:19,840
Good morning, Master.

243
00:18:19,840 --> 00:18:22,890
Oh Teacher you're up really early.

244
00:18:22,890 --> 00:18:24,930
Get ready to depart at once.

245
00:18:24,930 --> 00:18:26,100
Where to?

246
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:27,350
I'll explain later.

247
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,600
Hurry.

248
00:18:31,150 --> 00:18:32,400
Okay.

249
00:18:34,070 --> 00:18:34,820
Here!

250
00:18:35,690 --> 00:18:36,900
Whoa...

251
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:47,950
This kingdom is threatened by the Assyr Kingdom.

252
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:53,250
The prince of Assyr said he would invade this
country unless Princess Chime married him.

253
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:55,210
What a horrible story!

254
00:18:55,210 --> 00:18:56,710
Faye-chan is really mad about it.

255
00:18:56,710 --> 00:19:00,930
The king, unable to give up his beloved
daughter, was planning to refuse,

256
00:19:00,930 --> 00:19:03,590
which would mean an all-out
war between the kingdoms.

257
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,970
But Assyr is strong.

258
00:19:04,970 --> 00:19:07,680
If war broke out this kingdom
wouldn't stand a chance.

259
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:09,270
I understand.

260
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:14,060
So when Master appeared, he helped Chime
reach a decision about the wedding.

261
00:19:14,060 --> 00:19:16,770
She believes that with Master
around, this kingdom is safe.

262
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:18,110
That's exactly right.

263
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:21,400
The princess just left on a ship for the enemy kingdom.

264
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:33,500
You're a man, aren't you!?

265
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:35,460
Take some responsibility for your actions!

266
00:19:42,050 --> 00:19:43,890
I can't even help Chime.

267
00:19:43,890 --> 00:19:45,680
How can I be the legendary Black Angel?

268
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:47,470
Oh, Teacher?

269
00:19:47,470 --> 00:19:50,980
Maybe we could catch up with her ship if we left now?

270
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:52,640
Master! I know a way.

271
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:57,570
You have yet use teleportation.

272
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:59,110
That's right!

273
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:00,150
Teleportation!

274
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,360
How do I do it?

275
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,240
Tell me, please!

276
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:05,070
Place the feelings of the person
you wish to see in your heart.

277
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:07,280
Then you will fly to her side in an instant.

278
00:20:07,580 --> 00:20:08,620
Good!

279
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,370
Then I'll go too.

280
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:16,920
Big Sis!

281
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:20,250
Ah, how dare they leave me all by myself!

282
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:21,670
What a little whiner you are.

283
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:22,380
Come with me.

284
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:46,700
Come, young lady, why are you crying?

285
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,580
Angel?

286
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:51,200
I've come to rescue you, Chime.

287
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:53,660
Let's go.

288
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,540
Yes!

289
00:20:55,670 --> 00:21:00,210
Master? The point from which you teleported just
experienced an inter-dimensional power surge.

290
00:21:00,210 --> 00:21:02,590
You're trapped inhere!

291
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:04,220
You think I care about that?

292
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:07,550
It's time to punish those who tried to
use this sweet lady to start a war!

293
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:11,010
Ren, you take Chime back to Vineria.

294
00:21:11,850 --> 00:21:14,140
Yes, Master. Come, this way.

295
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:15,270
Please be careful.

296
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:22,110
Now, let's test these "powers" of mine
to see how far they stretch!

297
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,220
He killed them.

298
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:49,800
Now it's my fault.

299
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:01,900
How can I possibly thank you?

300
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:04,530
Thanks to you, Vineria has been saved.

301
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:08,030
Though I fear I can't control my own powers...

302
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:10,740
All's well that ends well.

303
00:22:10,740 --> 00:22:13,580
Father, I have a favor to ask.

304
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:17,250
What is it Chime? Ask me anything.

305
00:22:17,250 --> 00:22:20,500
I want to stay with the Angel.

306
00:22:25,090 --> 00:22:28,510
When I met the Angel I understood it clearly.

307
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,760
Even a princess, such as myself tied to a kingdom...

308
00:22:30,760 --> 00:22:33,180
has the right to love someone.

309
00:22:34,810 --> 00:22:36,770
"Love", you say? Umm...

310
00:22:36,770 --> 00:22:39,770
Very well said! You make your father proud!

311
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:41,810
You also say some pretty bold things, don't you?

312
00:22:55,700 --> 00:23:00,120
Chime-chan, it's so cool that you're
getting married on a spaceship!

313
00:23:00,670 --> 00:23:04,790
My beloved Angel says he wishes to depart
on a journey to retrieve his memories.

314
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:08,050
I want to do anything I can to help.

315
00:23:08,050 --> 00:23:09,050
Chime...

316
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:12,760
And helping my Angel retrieve his
happiness is also my happiness.

317
00:23:12,760 --> 00:23:18,640
Aw, Teacher! Please give Faye-chan
another training exercise!

318
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,230
Hey...

319
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:23,810
Master, I have a strange sensation.

320
00:23:23,810 --> 00:23:27,820
Are these "feelings," you think?

321
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:31,320
Looks like you learned a lot Ren.

322
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:35,320
I still couldn't find my own answer, though.

323
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,450
I don't get it.

324
00:23:37,450 --> 00:23:39,290
Didn't I tell you?

325
00:23:39,620 --> 00:23:41,580
You're the Dark Devil.

326
00:23:41,580 --> 00:23:42,580
You can only destroy and kill.

327
00:23:42,580 --> 00:23:44,040
You're the most evil thing in the universe.

328
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,460
Ms. Policewoman? What are you doing here?

329
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,800
Oh, shut your mouth.

330
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:51,470
I'm just keeping an eye on you to make
sure you don't remember anything.

331
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,840
This is part of my job.

332
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:56,050
You...

333
00:23:59,810 --> 00:24:01,520
By the way...

334
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,980
Who in the world am I?

335
00:24:04,310 --> 00:24:07,310
Who am If?

336
00:24:34,290 --> 00:24:38,550
ikiru tte muzukashii
Life sure is tough.

337
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:42,920
atama o kakae taku naru ne
Makes you wanna hold your head in shame.

338
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:47,930
zenbu nagedashite dokoka tooku e
I wanna throw everything far away,

339
00:24:47,970 --> 00:24:51,680
nige dashitai
and escape somewhere.

340
00:24:52,810 --> 00:24:57,190
suna o kamu you na hibi ga
These gritty days,

341
00:24:57,520 --> 00:25:01,610
zutto tsuzuite yuku you de
seem to go on forever.

342
00:25:01,900 --> 00:25:06,570
kokoro o sokunaru jibun no mirai
My unseen future pains my heart.

343
00:25:06,610 --> 00:25:10,330
nee dou naru no
Hey, what's gonna happen?

344
00:25:11,290 --> 00:25:14,210
rashii to kimaran'nakute mo
Even if I can't decide what's most like me,

345
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:20,550
kakko warukute mo kamawanai
and even if I look stupid, I don't care.

346
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,930
yaruki ga mondai
It's a matter of spirit;

347
00:25:23,430 --> 00:25:26,110
yaru koto ga daiji
doing things is important.

348
00:25:26,130 --> 00:25:30,260
nee sou deshou
Hey, isn't that so?

349
00:25:32,560 --> 00:25:36,900
yume no tane o makou yo
Let's spread the seeds of dreams,

350
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:41,150
suteki ni sodatta hanara
and raise them to be beautiful flowers,

351
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:45,530
kakae kirenai hodo no
in a bouquet too big to hold.

352
00:25:45,530 --> 00:25:51,120
shiawase no hanagara
A bouquet of flowers of happiness.

